  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This project plans on a training intervention by using public spaces and urban walkable
      trails, adapted to each patient needs and capabilities. Primary objective is to assess 12
      months effectiveness of the intervention with respect to: (primary outcome): physical
      activity level, and (secondary outcomes): COPD admissions, exercise capacity, body
      composition, quality of life, and mental health.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
